<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>You've Been Invited to TektonX</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    .header { background: #0f172a; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header img { height: 36px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #4f46e5); padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .hero p { color: #ede9fe; margin: 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h2 { color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .body p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin: 12px 0; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; margin: 24px 0 8px; padding: 12px 28px; background: #7c3aed; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; }
    .expiry-note { background: #fef9c3; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e; margin: 16px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 40px; background: #f8fafc; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#0f172a;"><tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#0f172a" style="padding:28px 40px;">
      <img src="{{frontendUrl}}/logo-white-horizontal.svg" alt="TektonX" style="height:72px;width:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;" />
    </td></tr></table>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#7c3aed" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#4f46e5);padding:24px 40px;">
      <p style="color:#ede9fe;margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;">You've been personally selected to join the TektonX mentorship program.</p>
    </td></tr></table>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Welcome, {{name}}!</h2>
      <span class="badge">Invited</span>
      <p>You've been invited to join TektonX as a mentee. Click the button below to set your password and activate your account.</p>
      <div class="expiry-note">
        This activation link expires in <strong>7 days</strong>. Please activate your account before it expires.
      </div>
      <a href="{{activateUrl}}" class="btn">Activate My Account</a>
      <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
        <a href="{{activateUrl}}" style="color:#7c3aed;">{{activateUrl}}</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you believe this invitation was sent in error, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#f8fafc" style="background:#f8fafc;padding:20px 40px;">
      <p style="color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;margin:0;">&copy; {{year}} TektonX Labs. All rights reserved.</p>
    </td></tr></table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
